Bir dugumden ulasilabilen tum dugumler.

```python
def reachable_nodes(graph,bas):
    visited=set(); stack=[bas]
    while stack:
        u=stack.pop()
        if u in visited: continue
        visited.add(u)
        for v in graph[u]:
            if v not in visited: stack.append(v)
    return visited

g={0:[1,2],1:[3],2:[3,4],3:[4],4:[]}
print(reachable_nodes(g,0))  # {0,1,2,3,4}
print(reachable_nodes(g,3))  # {3,4}
```

